AttributeBegin
LightSource "distant" "color L" [250 250 250 ] "point from" [0.0 1.0 0.0] "point to" [0.0 0.0 0.0]
AttributeEnd

AttributeBegin
Material "matte" "color Kd" [.9 .5 .5]
Translate 0 2 -.3
